# Source:
# https://css-tricks.com/words-avoid-educational-writing/
obviously	It might not be obvious to every reader.
basically	Even on an abstract level an explanation works better without 'basically'.
simply	It might be simple but it reads better without it.
of\scourse	Explain why explicitly instead of implicitly. Also helps to avoid errors.
clearly	If it is clear it doesn't need to be mentioned.
just	Casual.
everyone\sknows	Not everyone knows, explain explicitly instead of implicitly.
so,	Transitional, a new paragraph might suit better.
easy	Casual.
